The '''Pentastar Patrol Academy''' was an officer training school for the [[Pentastar Patrol|Enforcement branch]] of the [[Pentastar Alignment]]. It accepted nonhumans, a fact that brought much consternation to its formerly-[[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] heads.

